sentences: Beatriz Bilbao (born 8 December 1951) is a Venezuelan composer.

In 1991 she took a teaching position at the Instituto Universitario de Estudios Musicales (IUDEM) in Caracas and from 2001–02  served as director of the Ministry of Culture's Prudencio Esáa Music School.
